Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.51,0:00:06.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Just run you have to go the police are on
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.91,0:00:13.05,Default,,0,0,0,,The Public Square by the station
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.31,0:00:16.64,Default,,0,0,0,,There
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.92,0:00:18.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Give me the message
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.25,0:00:22.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Here it is
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.83,0:00:25.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Bridge
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.60,0:00:29.18,Default,,0,0,0,,And the three frogs my father said something else also
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.95,0:00:31.74,Default,,0,0,0,,If the monster that you're chasing
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.00,0:00:33.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Happens to have a twin
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.05,0:00:36.61,Default,,0,0,0,,The mother of those same twins
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.38,0:00:42.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Is still alive and Brock
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.27,0:02:32.57,Default,,0,0,0,,So Mr Grimmer have any luck
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.83,0:02:35.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you find some of the information you were looking for
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.16,0:02:38.21,Default,,0,0,0,,What's your after won't be easy to locate
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.46,0:02:41.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Record keeping changed when the East and West United
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.28,0:02:43.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Data from before then it's hard to find
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.84,0:02:46.14,Default,,0,0,0,,My thank you for this opportunity principal
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.91,0:02:49.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Frankly I'm surprised you have even this much left
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.98,0:02:50.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Most
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.01,0:02:51.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Far less
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.54,0:02:54.08,Default,,0,0,0,,And of course you're quite correct
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.59,0:02:55.87,Default,,0,0,0,,When the Berlin Wall fell
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.13,0:03:00.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Almost all of the data involving East Germany's unsavory practices disappeared forever
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.74,0:03:01.25,Default,,0,0,0,,You know
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.02,0:03:07.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel quite sure that the children in the orphanages of the oldies Germany were victims of physical and mental abuse
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.42,0:03:13.54,Default,,0,0,0,,But of course the real challenge here is actually finding any written records to prove my thoughts are true
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.05,0:03:15.59,Default,,0,0,0,,You're thinking sounds right
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.84,0:03:21.22,Default,,0,0,0,,You know most of East Germany's orphanages were being managed under the jurisdiction of the Ministry of Health and Welfare
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.98,0:03:28.12,Default,,0,0,0,,But a much bigger problem was created when the authorities classified a child's parents as criminal offenders political prisoners
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.38,0:03:30.68,Default,,0,0,0,,There's spies or even illegal immigrants
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.20,0:03:37.34,Default,,0,0,0,,In the midst of all of the orphanages that took care of these children there was one special orphanage run by the notorious internal
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.60,0:03:38.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Affairs Ministry
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.88,0:03:44.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Apparently there were many instances of abuse and these inhumane personality Corrections took place
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.51,0:03:46.05,Default,,0,0,0,,At one particular orphanage
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.56,0:03:48.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyhow that's what I want to find out
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.61,0:03:50.15,Default,,0,0,0,,And as much detail as possible
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.40,0:03:53.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to know every last little thing that happened there
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.47,0:03:55.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm leaving no stone unturned
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.78,0:03:57.83,Default,,0,0,0,,My that's a tedious task huh
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.34,0:04:01.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd like to help but there's not much information to share
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.92,0:04:06.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Most of those involved have passed away kept silent or their leading new lives
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.53,0:04:07.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure you're right
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.81,0:04:13.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Even Mr schner who's now an instructor here won't speak with me wait did you say Mr schner
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.70,0:04:18.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes he was a teacher at East Germany's 62 kinderheim under the old regime
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.56,0:04:20.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I requested interview I'm about his past but
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.12,0:04:22.40,Default,,0,0,0,,You refused my request
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.17,0:04:23.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.94,0:04:30.08,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a real possibility Mr terrorized children while he worked in East Germany so I'd be a little more cautious around him
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.34,0:04:30.85,Default,,0,0,0,,If I were you
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.94,0:04:40.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh would it be all right if I photocopied some of the information in these books sure that would be just fine
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.34,0:04:46.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr Grimmer if I may you are a newspaper journalist from West Germany isn't that correct
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.49,0:04:48.77,Default,,0,0,0,,No I'm from this side
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.02,0:04:51.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Well I work as a reporter for a newspaper in leip
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.10,0:04:52.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Well
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.86,0:04:56.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I never expected a human rights Advocate like you to be from the Eastern BL
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.96,0:04:57.98,Default,,0,0,0,,It's true
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.01,0:05:03.87,Default,,0,0,0,,During that time I used to travel all over the world as a special overseas news correspond
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.74,0:05:11.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah I went everywhere on missions for the government
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.06,0:05:12.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you understand
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.62,0:05:15.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I used to be a spy
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.70,0:05:21.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Here we go
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.79,0:05:23.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Goodness you're back looks awfully heavy
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.10,0:05:27.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Well it's packed with all the data I've collected traveling around East Germany
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.45,0:05:30.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't wait to read up on your findings
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.75,0:05:34.33,Default,,0,0,0,,So where are you heading to Next oh to the Czech Republic
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.10,0:05:35.87,Default,,0,0,0,,On to PR
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.38,0:05:37.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for all your help principal
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.82,0:05:58.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard you getting treated pretty badly by those boys
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.68,0:06:02.50,Default,,0,0,0,,And they ended up taking your shoes away didn't they
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.01,0:06:04.29,Default,,0,0,0,,You know crying won't help
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.60,0:06:21.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey you know what it's been proven that people can live without shoes
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.46,0:06:25.02,Default,,0,0,0,,After all every last one of us was born barefoot
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.54,0:06:26.82,Default,,0,0,0,,But I must say
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.35,0:06:31.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyone who bullies other people by stealing their shoes
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.19,0:06:33.21,Default,,0,0,0,,They're the worst
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.47,0:06:37.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyhow now you have shoes again so there's no need to cry anymore
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.82,0:06:38.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Take care
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.54,0:07:02.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm guessing they're a little big for you am I right
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.66,0:07:17.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me sir
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.53,0:07:21.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you have a second sir of course what is it
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.37,0:07:23.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm kind of in a fix
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.16,0:07:25.95,Default,,0,0,0,,You see I have a big problem
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.21,0:07:30.05,Default,,0,0,0,,My briefcase that had my passport and it was stolen just a while ago
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.30,0:07:33.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Your passport was stolen not really is a big problem
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.89,0:07:39.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I turned around and it was gone I'm on my way to see my younger sister who lives in Vienna
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.52,0:07:43.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Only yesterday I got a phone call saying that she suddenly collapsed
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.62,0:07:44.64,Default,,0,0,0,,She collapsed
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.90,0:07:47.20,Default,,0,0,0,,You need to find a way to get there as soon as possible
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.46,0:07:52.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are the police maybe they can help you I already talked to them
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.32,0:07:55.90,Default,,0,0,0,,The bigger problem is my poor sister doesn't have any money for a doctor
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.16,0:07:58.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh no that's got to be the worst news yet
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.72,0:08:02.30,Default,,0,0,0,,And the top things off my stolen briefcase had my wallet in it too
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.07,0:08:03.58,Default,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.84,0:08:09.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I know I can't go but if I could at least find a way to water some money to my sister she could get some medical attention but now
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.24,0:08:16.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Now it's looking like I can't even do that so just how much do you need oh no no no you don't need to help out
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.64,0:08:18.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Honestly I don't need that much money really
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.94,0:08:23.55,Default,,0,0,0,,All I need is to pull together a small amount of cash just enough so she can see a doctor
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.06,0:08:26.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Here I'm just sorry I don't have more to give you
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.88,0:08:31.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh thank you sir don't question I swear that I'll pay you back very soon
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.26,0:08:35.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Just write down the address where you want me to send the check
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.33,0:08:37.12,Default,,0,0,0,,That's all right no need to repay me
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.38,0:08:39.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Just see that your sister gets the help she needs okay
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.45,0:08:41.47,Default,,0,0,0,,God bless you sir
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.73,0:08:45.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you so much I wish you and your sister all the best
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.08,0:08:49.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on Daddy how could you hand over your money to that Hustler
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.66,0:08:52.48,Default,,0,0,0,,He was lying and story was just a scam
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.74,0:08:53.51,Default,,0,0,0,,A scam
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.76,0:08:59.90,Default,,0,0,0,,That guy works as train station all the time looking for suckers like you I can't believe you got fooled
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.16,0:09:00.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Play that Hustler
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.98,0:09:04.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I really got fooled
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.51,0:09:10.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Attention the express training frog will be departing
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.91,0:09:15.01,Default,,0,0,0,,3:15 p.m.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.52,0:09:18.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn it
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.58,0:09:30.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't think it was going to make it for a sec
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.14,0:09:32.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks for your help you're welcome
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.78,0:09:53.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey thanks again for earlier do you mind if I sit here no go ahead
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.37,0:10:03.91,Default,,0,0,0,,So where are you headed
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.16,0:10:06.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh man I'm headed for Prague
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.78,0:10:25.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm guessing you're Japanese am I right
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.18,0:10:32.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Konichiwa oh dumb you know I visited Japan a couple of times
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.58,0:10:38.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh how long has it been since I was there last well it's been a couple of years I can tell you
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.98,0:10:45.12,Default,,0,0,0,,That much the last time I was over there was a business trip but I went to Akihabara to purchase some wiretap equipment
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.38,0:10:51.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Another high-tech gadgets oh yeah that reminds me this song it was really popular I'm sure you know
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.78,0:10:57.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh talk about dorino
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.18,0:11:04.32,Default,,0,0,0,,No no that's not right you keep tunnel soccer
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.58,0:11:10.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh that's right that's how it goes tunnel
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.98,0:11:17.12,Default,,0,0,0,,My son would have loved it if I
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.38,0:11:23.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Brought back a plastic model toy for him so where's your son now oh he's gone
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.78,0:11:29.92,Default,,0,0,0,,My son died
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.18,0:11:36.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Departure passport check if you would present your pass
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.34,0:11:39.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh sure I love course
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.00,0:11:47.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Danke Schoen
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.73,0:11:59.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Look there's the Elder River how's the trout fishing
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.13,0:12:04.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Been on the Elba River this year anyway it hasn't been very good sir
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.48,0:12:10.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh is that so cuz last year I caught a trout this big on that river that wouldn't happen this
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.88,0:12:17.02,Default,,0,0,0,,This year Duncan sir
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.68,0:12:29.82,Default,,0,0,0,,He's on to the fact that was a fake passport you just showed him
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.18,0:12:40.32,Default,,0,0,0,,You need to get moving right now Dr Tema how is it that you know who I am that's not
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.58,0:12:46.72,Default,,0,0,0,,What does matter here is that the Border Police have realized your passports are fake and I'm sure they're on their way
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.98,0:12:49.80,Default,,0,0,0,,So you need to get out of here right now doctor Tenma
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.43,0:13:12.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Move it you come on we need to get past you sorry about this guys
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.83,0:13:18.97,Default,,0,0,0,,My duffel bag so big and overstuffed I guess I'm kind of stuck here I can't seem to move get out of the way right now
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.23,0:13:25.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Believe me sir I am trying to get out of the way what's in that bag anyway some very valuable
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.03,0:13:38.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Good I finally got loose
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.43,0:13:44.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you know where that other man went to me there was an Asian man who was sitting with you in this comp
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.83,0:13:50.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah you're right well maybe he got hungry and went to the dining car movement
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.23,0:13:57.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Passenger car too we have an Asian man using a fake passport who's running loose on his
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.63,0:14:03.77,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.89,0:14:31.68,Default,,0,0,0,,You did very well back there
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.22,0:14:34.50,Default,,0,0,0,,They're not chasing us
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.75,0:14:36.03,Default,,0,0,0,,They're searching the other way
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.80,0:14:39.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Since the train was stopped I figured I should get off
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.13,0:14:42.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh I guess I forgot to introduce myself doctor
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.94,0:14:43.96,Default,,0,0,0,,My name is Grimmer
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.02,0:14:51.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought you might need some guidance doctor 10 minutes so if you'd like I could show you the way to the Border
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.66,0:15:04.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm very well acquainted with this area
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.70,0:15:10.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually I fished around here quite a few times it's mountainous terrain so the hike ain't easy but the view
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.15,0:15:13.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Grimmer
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.43,0:15:15.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did you help me anyway
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.04,0:15:22.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Well you see I worked for a newspaper company in East Germany
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.62,0:15:24.16,Default,,0,0,0,,But now I'm doing my own
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.67,0:15:25.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Freelance journalist
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.98,0:15:32.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I've read every article about you I could find and I have to admit I find you very interesting
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.86,0:15:36.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Being falsely accused of crimes was a part of everyday life in East Germany
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.47,0:15:39.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Political prisoners charged without Merit
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.54,0:15:42.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Accused murderers who weren't really guilty
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.10,0:15:44.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Seeing that happen all the time
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.15,0:15:49.25,Default,,0,0,0,,You got to have a pretty good eye for spotting who was guilty and who was innocent
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.78,0:15:52.32,Default,,0,0,0,,And I'd say you're innocent
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.58,0:15:54.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Does that sound about right doctor ten
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.67,0:15:59.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen do me a favor and stop calling me doctor
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.26,0:16:00.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.54,0:16:05.89,Default,,0,0,0,,But doctor Tenma you're one of the world's most brilliant neurosurgeons aren't you proud of that
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.14,0:16:07.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I am no longer a doctor
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.64,0:16:18.18,Default,,0,0,0,,So
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.43,0:16:19.45,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you think
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.97,0:16:22.02,Default,,0,0,0,,The Magnificent view isn't it
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.78,0:16:26.11,Default,,0,0,0,,And from here we can see anyone coming up the mountain after us
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.90,0:16:31.74,Default,,0,0,0,,That said I think we've earned a well-deserved break for lunch
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.05,0:16:36.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Would you care to join me for a sandwich
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.35,0:16:38.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I also brought a rather nice red wine
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.66,0:16:40.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh and some delicious cheese
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.22,0:16:42.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for your offer
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.75,0:16:44.54,Default,,0,0,0,,But I really need to keep on moving
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.57,0:16:47.11,Default,,0,0,0,,It's hours until sunset
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.36,0:16:50.43,Default,,0,0,0,,It'll be easier and safer trying to cross the border after Dark
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.46,0:16:57.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Eating outside like this
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.86,0:16:58.63,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just the best
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.14,0:17:02.47,Default,,0,0,0,,It's such a treat to do this once in awhile isn't it Dr tema
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.23,0:17:06.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Enjoying delicious food while taking in a wonderful View
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.58,0:17:12.19,Default,,0,0,0,,It's moments like this that help me truly feel the pleasures of living
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.24,0:17:20.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I must admit I have a profound respect for you doctors journalists like myself served entertain people
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.64,0:17:24.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Hopefully my readers feel happier to be alive after reading my articles
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.74,0:17:25.76,Default,,0,0,0,,But what you do
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.02,0:17:29.60,Default,,0,0,0,,That's powerful you literally give people life
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.14,0:17:32.42,Default,,0,0,0,,But I
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.46,0:17:35.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Shot a man
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.74,0:17:37.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I did it on purpose
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.75,0:17:48.54,Default,,0,0,0,,It happened last month in mun
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.31,0:17:51.10,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the first time I shot someone
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.15,0:17:54.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I think he probably died
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.74,0:17:59.30,Default,,0,0,0,,My hands were trembling so much I couldn't name
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.06,0:18:01.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I think I'd really be able to do it
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.39,0:18:04.41,Default,,0,0,0,,But after I shot him
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.70,0:18:06.98,Default,,0,0,0,,My hand stopped Tre
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.10,0:18:12.87,Default,,0,0,0,,And now
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.63,0:18:15.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I know that I have to shoot another man
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.19,0:18:18.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I have to stop a man that's pure evil
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.31,0:18:22.59,Default,,0,0,0,,One thing is for certain
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.36,0:18:24.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not doctor
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.26,0:18:44.36,Default,,0,0,0,,When I see the Elbow River I think of how I'd give anything to change the past
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.86,0:18:49.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah I would have made a difference so I could have shared the joy of fishing here with my son
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.01,0:18:52.80,Default,,0,0,0,,What was he like your little boy
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.08,0:18:56.38,Default,,0,0,0,,You can catch a trout this big in that River
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.41,0:19:01.25,Default,,0,0,0,,My poor son died without me ever sharing the pleasures of the outdoors with him
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.27,0:19:05.60,Default,,0,0,0,,What makes me the saddest is feeling that his life could have been saved
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.62,0:19:09.18,Default,,0,0,0,,If a doctor like you had been there for him
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.54,0:19:17.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I swear you can catch trout this big I'm not kidding around here
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.57,0:19:29.67,Default,,0,0,0,,The other side of that mountain is the check border
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.69,0:19:34.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Follow the force path pass there and you'll hit a road where you might be able to get a ride
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.55,0:19:38.11,Default,,0,0,0,,As for me I'm heading back to the train station now
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.37,0:19:42.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you Mr Grimmer I never would have made it this far without you helping me
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.49,0:19:45.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I truly wish you the best of luck
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.79,0:19:46.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Dr
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.12,0:19:53.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Say if we meet again let's plan for another great picnic all right
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.92,0:20:03.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey doctor Tenma
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.02,0:20:08.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone in this world carries around their own sins
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.09,0:20:10.37,Default,,0,0,0,,And they never go away
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.88,0:20:13.70,Default,,0,0,0,,But that doesn't change the fact that we do what we must
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.14,0:20:46.47,Default,,0,0,0,,How wonderful
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.74,0:20:53.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd always heard this was a beautiful city this may be my first night in Prague but I'm already Enchanted it's like a village
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.14,0:20:58.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Message from a fairy tale
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.69,0:21:08.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me do you mind if I sit here
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.25,0:21:15.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Search yourself I must say I'm completely
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.65,0:21:17.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Captivated by this city
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.70,0:21:23.08,Default,,0,0,0,,You're Mr pedrov Right you bought your Russian citizenship and now here you are
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.33,0:21:24.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Living in Prague
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.61,0:21:30.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd like to ask you some things about your past sir would you be willing to help me with some answers Mr
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.01,0:21:31.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Pedro
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.78,0:21:35.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh my mistake your real name is reinhard-beerman isn't it
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.92,0:21:41.50,Default,,0,0,0,,There was this very special orphanage located in East Berlin right
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.76,0:21:46.62,Default,,0,0,0,,It was more of a laboratory really we're experiments were conducted on children's personalities
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.39,0:21:49.44,Default,,0,0,0,,It was called 511 kinderh
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.95,0:21:55.84,Default,,0,0,0,,And you were the director there Mr bierma
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.10,0:21:58.66,Default,,0,0,0,,You should know all about the abuse that went on there
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.91,0:22:01.47,Default,,0,0,0,,After all sir you were the one running the place
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.24,0:22:05.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Just what were you trying to achieve in those experiments
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.82,0:22:07.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Back in East Berlin
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.36,0:22:13.50,Default,,0,0,0,,511 kinderheim care to explain it to me
